The day is not over and gifts are still rolling out!  There are a lot of accounts, so it will take some time per our [support banner](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/227317608--Sept-14-Anniversary-gifts-are-currently-being-distributed-You-may-not-receive-them-right-away-so-please-be-patient-). Give it until the end of the day. They are still being distributed per the banner on the [support page](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us).
